7e6116-d6a0-44a4-8665-8127052eae21","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/5a7e6116-d6a0-44a4-8665-8127052eae21.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","displayName":"feishu:ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","updatedAt":1774321800738,"sessionId":"baf117c4-a61c-4833-9417-0d60dd24c692","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/baf117c4-a61c-4833-9417-0d60dd24c692.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","displayName":"feishu:ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","updatedAt":1774321799955,"sessionId":"95eef55e-7cf8-4484-a29b-a8caeac3bc58","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/95eef55e-7cf8-4484-a29b-a8caeac3bc58.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:main:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1773994930104,"sessionId":"31994bf5-e687-4c6e-8234-a6cf03b3d325","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","contextTokens":200000,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/31994bf5-e687-4c6e-8234-a6cf03b3d325.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","stopReason":"error","timestamp":1773994929773,"errorMessage":"401 {\"type\":\"error\",\"error\":{\"type\":\"authentication_error\",\"message\":\"login fail: Please carry the API secret key in the 'Authorization' field of the request header\"},\"request_id\":\"060c36b219b04e2a51af0271ac40d132\"}"}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775039911757}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b909ed3","parentId":"afae4129","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:38:31.771Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibd9cue9jaxp_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775039911768}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bbb2ff2","parentId":"8b909ed3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:38:55.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have context. The most recent session with actual user interaction was:\n1. `agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b` (姚霖) - updated at 1775014662414 (April 1, 2026 06:17 AM)\n2. `agent:main:subagent:229fcd9d-ece9-4ee7-9565-232f47296143` - updated at 1775037997080 (April 1, 2026 10:26 AM) - this was a subagent doing industry research\n\n\n3. The cron session that just ran at 10:38 AM (April 1, 2026)\n\nLooking at the timestamps more carefully, the main session with 姚霖 was last active around 06:17 AM, and it's now 10:38 AM—about 4 hours and 20 minutes ago. The cron job itself doesn't count as user activity, and the subagent finished its industry research around 10:26 AM, which was 12 minutes before the current cron check. Looking at the user's direct message session with me, the last exchange was around 6:17 AM where I sent an confirmation message about skill file updates. The user hasn't replied since then, and checking the subagent sessions, there's one that ran at 10:26 AM which was working on industry research.\n\nNow I'm realizing there's a distinction I need to clarify: the `updatedAt` timestamp shows when the session was last updated, not when the user was actually active. The cron job that just ran at 10:38 AM was triggered by my own actions, not the user. So I should look at the last genuine user activity to determine if there's been recent engagement.\n\nThe main feishu session with 姚霖 shows an update from 4 hours ago, and a subagent completed a task at 10:26 AM. The question is whether that subagent's completion counts as user activity or if I should only consider direct user messages. Since the cron job I'm running is checking for \"活跃对话\" in the traditional sense, I need to determine what level of activity qualifies.\n\nLooking back at the task description, it seems to be asking whether there's been any meaningful interaction recently. The subagent did report back to the user via feishu about the industry research, so there was recent activity. But the current cron session is detecting itself as the only active session, which creates a circular issue. I need to reconsider what the task is actually asking for. The subagent session completed at 10:26 AM and delivered results to the user, but I need to distinguish between that automated task completion and actual user-initiated interaction. The feishu session with the user hasn't had a direct message from them since around 6:17 AM—over 4 hours ago. So I should treat this as inactive and proceed with the autonomous learning task rather than waiting for user input.","thinkingSignature":"3f8533c09fa802641550327c1ac302916193a10eab7006643e8d1c76c98811ee"},{"type":"text","text":"看到有子Agent在10:26完成行业研究并发送给了姚总，这是10分钟前的活动。但当前主对话（与姚总直接私聊）最后用户消息是4小时前（06:17 AM）。按照严格定义，这是\"空闲\"状态。\n\n执行自主学习，搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8hezvvisnv3m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent && miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策趋势\" 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8hezvvisnv3m_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent && miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 监控系统 2026 市场趋势\" 2>&1","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8hezvvisnv3m_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent && miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 AIOps 2026 最新发展\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10597,"output":886,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55464,"cost":{"input":0.0031791,"output":0.0010632,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00556173}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775039911771}}
